data.description: Home with acrerage! Seller has made lots of upgrades to the property including a metal roof in 2017 and a new 5 ton heat pump.  In 2018 they installed a 20x30 detached garage.  There is a 16 x 20 building that is insulated with electricity and has a window heat & air unit. Park your boat and camper under the 20 x 30 carport.  There is fencing around all 2.5 areas.  This home comes with 2 water wells and 1 has a culligan water softner installed. Seller also installed  rain gutters and french drains front and back of house.  They have also replaced all water lines inside the house with the control box located in the laundry room/ office. Kitchen cabinets and dishwasher have been replaced within the last year. There is an acre lot next to door to the house that goes with this property. Run your livestock there or it could be a build site.
